                        "Id" : "outcome_0_0",
                        "Name" : "FinalStand",
                        "Details" : "Just as hope seemed to dwindle, a familiar voice crackled over my coms. \"Zeroed in on the vermin,\" came the steady tone of [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]].\r\n\r\nIn the next instant, a barrage of slammed into the enemy Locust, courtesy of [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]]'s {SCN_UNIT.Name} BattleMech. The force of the alpha strike overwhelmed the Locust, sending it crashing to the ground in a heap of twisted metal.\r\n\r\nThe raiders outside began to panic, their earlier bravado evaporating in the face of rescue forces from Argo. The inexperienced pilot of the Locust scrambled out of the fallen 'Mech, abandoning it in sheer terror.\r\n\r\n\r\nAs the dust settled, [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]]'s voice boomed over the external speakers. \"Did you guys find any meat on this forsaken planet? I'm so tired of potatoes.\"\r\n\r\n \"Negative. Just trouble. Thanks for the save,\" [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] answers.\r\n\r\n\"Figures,\" [[TRT_MW,{TRT_MW.Callsign}]] sighed. \"Let's get you back to the Argo.\"",
